    {
      "id": "task-creator",
      "name": "Task Creator",
      "description": "Meta-task: Create a new agent task template",
      "icon": "Wand",
      "color": "#f5c76b",
      "prompt": "Create a detailed task template for the following task: {{description}}\n\nThe template should include:\n- An appropriate name and description\n- The main prompt with any necessary variable placeholders using {{variableName}} syntax\n- Appropriate CLI flags (model, maxTurns, print mode, etc.)\n- Any useful pre-commands or post-commands\n- Variable definitions with descriptions\n\nOutput the template as a JSON object that matches this structure:\n{\n  \"name\": \"...\",\n  \"description\": \"...\",\n  \"prompt\": \"...\",\n  \"cliFlags\": { ... },\n  \"variables\": [ ... ],\n  \"preCommands\": [ ... ],\n  \"postCommands\": [ ... ]\n}",
      "cliFlags": {
        "print": true,
        "model": "opus"
      },
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "description",
          "description": "Description of the task you want to create",
          "required": true
        },
        {
          "name": "cli_ref",
          "description": "reference to available cli commands",
          "required": false
        }
      ],
      "preCommands": [],
      "postCommands": [],
      "createdAt": "2025-12-04T01:04:37.013Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-12-04T01:23:54.166Z",
      "tags": [
        "meta",
        "automation"
      ]
    },
